title: Fruit Gallery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out only, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tiny takeaway shop just off the Venice Beach boardwalk. Has a small table in front for seating. Menu consists of a variety of smoothies in addition to fresh pressed juices and several choices of wraps as well as a raw food menu (raw tacos, spaghetti, enchilada). A refrigerator stocks whole coconuts and bottled drinks.
